<HH> ============= Screen: Introduction ======================== </HH>

<IntakeGate ready="!@fba2_completion_checkbox.value">
<Markdown> </Markdown>
<Markdown id="fba2_introduction">
## Introduction

In this module, you will continue helping Annie's roommate with Johnny, the 6-year-old she babysits. The positive reinforcement techniques from last time are partially working, but Johnny still runs away at bedtime.

In this session, you will review and apply several concepts from your coursework on behavior modification. Specifically, you will:

- Identify the **function of behavior** and the four main functions.
- Understand the **ABCs** (Antecedent, Behavior, Consequence) of behavior analysis.
- Develop an **intervention plan** using a Competing Behavior Pathway.
- Use an **AI Assistant** to support learning and problem solving.

Let's begin.
</Markdown>
</IntakeGate>


