<HH> ============= Screen: ABC reference diagram ================ </HH>

<IntakeGate ready="!@fba2_completion_checkbox.value">
<Markdown> </Markdown>
<Vertical id="fba2_abc_reference">
<Markdown>
## ABC Reference Diagrams

Each diagram shows the **Antecedent → Behavior → Consequence** chain for one function of behavior.
</Markdown>

<Markdown>### Escape (Negative Reinforcement)</Markdown>
<Mermaid id="fba2_abc_ref_escape"><![CDATA[
flowchart LR
  A["Antecedent:<br/>Teacher gives a difficult task"] --> B["Behavior:<br/>Student puts head down"] --> C["Consequence:<br/>Task is removed or delayed"]
  class A ant
  class B beh
  class C con
  classDef ant fill:#fff3cd,stroke:#ffc107,stroke-width:2px,color:#000
  classDef beh fill:#cfe2ff,stroke:#0d6efd,stroke-width:2px,color:#000
  classDef con fill:#d1e7dd,stroke:#198754,stroke-width:2px,color:#000
]]></Mermaid>

<Markdown>### Attention (Positive Reinforcement)</Markdown>
<Mermaid id="fba2_abc_ref_attention"><![CDATA[
flowchart LR
  A["Antecedent:<br/>Parent is on the phone"] --> B["Behavior:<br/>Child shouts loudly"] --> C["Consequence:<br/>Parent gives attention"]
  class A ant
  class B beh
  class C con
  classDef ant fill:#fff3cd,stroke:#ffc107,stroke-width:2px,color:#000
  classDef beh fill:#cfe2ff,stroke:#0d6efd,stroke-width:2px,color:#000
  classDef con fill:#d1e7dd,stroke:#198754,stroke-width:2px,color:#000
]]></Mermaid>

<Markdown>### Access/Tangible (Positive Reinforcement)</Markdown>
<Mermaid id="fba2_abc_ref_tangible"><![CDATA[
flowchart LR
  A["Antecedent:<br/>Toy is out of reach"] --> B["Behavior:<br/>Child cries"] --> C["Consequence:<br/>Parent gives the toy"]
  class A ant
  class B beh
  class C con
  classDef ant fill:#fff3cd,stroke:#ffc107,stroke-width:2px,color:#000
  classDef beh fill:#cfe2ff,stroke:#0d6efd,stroke-width:2px,color:#000
  classDef con fill:#d1e7dd,stroke:#198754,stroke-width:2px,color:#000
]]></Mermaid>

<Markdown>### Sensory (Automatic Reinforcement)</Markdown>
<Mermaid id="fba2_abc_ref_sensory"><![CDATA[
flowchart LR
  A["Antecedent:<br/>Quiet time with no stimulation"] --> B["Behavior:<br/>Child flaps hands"] --> C["Consequence:<br/>Self-stimulation feels good"]
  class A ant
  class B beh
  class C con
  classDef ant fill:#fff3cd,stroke:#ffc107,stroke-width:2px,color:#000
  classDef beh fill:#cfe2ff,stroke:#0d6efd,stroke-width:2px,color:#000
  classDef con fill:#d1e7dd,stroke:#198754,stroke-width:2px,color:#000
]]></Mermaid>
</Vertical>
</IntakeGate>


